Do you think to claim every piece matches the Oracle Saga? Do you dare to rob the saga of masterworks status?! Do you truly harbour such hubris?!

No heathen, I say no. Return to your exploitative sycophantism, while I return to my search for meaning and truth in the works of the RearSeer. 

Leave now Delphius, your works are naught and your heresy null.
